'''肿瘤浸润淋巴细胞'''（{{lang-en|Tumor-infiltrating lymphocytes}}，缩写'''TILs'''）是指已离开[[血液|血液]]向[[肿瘤|肿瘤]]组织[[细胞迁移|迁移]]的[[淋巴细胞|淋巴细胞]]，是'''肿瘤浸润免疫细胞'''（{{lang-en|tumor-infiltrating immune cells}}）这个更大的概念的一部分，后者还包括[[单核细胞|单核细胞]]和分叶核的免疫细胞。肿瘤中浸润的免疫细胞与临床结果密切相关，可作为治疗癌症的[[靶向药物|药物靶标]]。<ref name="Teixeira2016">{{cite journal|title=Breast Cancer Immunology|journal=Oncology Times|volume=38|issue=9|pages=18–19|doi=10.1097/01.COT.0000483221.52404.e3|year=2016|last1=Teixeira|first1=Luis|last2=Rothé|first2=Françoise|last3=Ignatiadis|first3=Michail|last4=Sotiriou|first4=Christos}}</ref><ref name="Hanahan2012">{{cite journal | vauthors = Hanahan D, Coussens LM | title = Accessories to the crime: functions of cells recruited to the tumor microenvironment | journal = Cancer Cell | volume = 21 | issue = 3 | pages = 309–22 | date = March 2012 | pmid = 22439926 | doi = 10.1016/j.ccr.2012.02.022 | doi-access = free }}</ref><ref name=":1">{{cite journal | vauthors = Coussens LM, Zitvogel L, Palucka AK | title = Neutralizing tumor-promoting chronic inflammation: a magic bullet? | journal = Science | volume = 339 | issue = 6117 | pages = 286–91 | date = January 2013 | pmid = 23329041 | pmc = 3591506 | doi = 10.1126/science.1232227 }}</ref><ref name=":2">{{cite journal | vauthors = Engblom C, Pfirschke C, Zilionis R, Da Silva Martins J, Bos SA, Courties G, Rickelt S, Severe N, Baryawno N, Faget J, Savova V, Zemmour D, Kline J, Siwicki M, Garris C, Pucci F, Liao HW, Lin YJ, Newton A, Yaghi OK, Iwamoto Y, Tricot B, Wojtkiewicz GR, Nahrendorf M, Cortez-Retamozo V, Meylan E, Hynes RO, Demay M, Klein A, Bredella MA, Scadden DT, Weissleder R, Pittet MJ | title = high neutrophils | journal = Science | volume = 358 | issue = 6367 | pages = eaal5081 | date = December 2017 | pmid = 29191879 | pmc = 6343476 | doi = 10.1126/science.aal5081 }}</ref><ref name=":3">{{cite journal | vauthors = Gentles AJ, Newman AM, Liu CL, Bratman SV, Feng W, Kim D, Nair VS, Xu Y, Khuong A, Hoang CD, Diehn M, West RB, Plevritis SK, Alizadeh AA | title = The prognostic landscape of genes and infiltrating immune cells across human cancers | journal = Nature Medicine | volume = 21 | issue = 8 | pages = 938–945 | date = August 2015 | pmid = 26193342 | pmc = 4852857 | doi = 10.1038/nm.3909 }}</ref>

